{"tid":211844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（地產狗）為答謝捐贈者，「帶著」捐贈者的肝臟圓其心願","createTime":"2017-04-22T02:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T04:52:21.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff4062f83d95a240811c48559b91340cfbca8ab","tid":211844,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"現年51歲的吳國偉&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;在中原地產任職25年，終成為資深區域營業董事，專責又一村、何文田區豪宅，掌管每年營業額可高逾一億港元的約一百人團隊，他形容以前的生活很忙、很急：「日日都很熱鬧，成群伙記圍著你，整天要出去做很多事」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「今次若不是有心人捐給我，我根本不能在活在此世界！」<span style=\"color: red;\">吳國偉為答謝捐贈者，得知她生前一直想到英國旅行，故打算康復後偕妻到訪英國，「帶著」捐贈者的肝臟圓其心願。</span>"},{"pid":"562212ab20016db3d67b505c9fcb9a74440ad4fa","tid":211844,"uid":47309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"佢老母..."},{"pid":"165559606c1122c3d7b61f3736717899fd98c8c9","tid":211844,"uid":16135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T02:56:05.000Z","msg":"我屌又係唔落sourse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40ca93400e41b97132109968b2f08d6fbc92d7f","tid":211844,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T02:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62c41951d906e5216ba2140247e8887a3f55a212","tid":211844,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T02:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢老母...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似帶住「戰利品」去巡遊咁！"},{"pid":"8d74568103fa6c72b5f3b23f7450e9b863f86296","tid":211844,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係唔落sourse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高登出新聞都唔落source啦，憑咩要思覺脫落source啊，呢啲係慣例嚟"},{"pid":"925e789611eb5d80f1fb5a7ed92973ffcea0e3ab","tid":211844,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04