情況係唔會知捐贈者身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30257efba258600c38baa1700d87781b023339ef","tid":211844,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好感恩，做埋d 唔肉痛既野，加個意義上去當係代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起碼都比左一百幾十萬人地啦</blockquote><br />\n好似正常情況係唔會知捐贈者身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家興「表揚」捐贈者架！"},{"pid":"71716e0cc4443a92feabc2c32f826f3cb0071e6f","tid":211844,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶著肝臟去旅行 yeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁同老婆扑野，係咪3p?"},{"pid":"036a279574a7f996ef9cbc685570576663b87dc7","tid":211844,"uid":66129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:53:56.000Z","msg":"我識佢老鼠咩"},{"pid":"b034db841dbb87baab51b9604cef39d2889133a8","tid":211844,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係唔落sourse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高登出新聞都唔落source啦，憑咩要思覺脫落source啊，呢啲係慣例嚟</blockquote><br />\n有d人有「潔癖」乜都要講原創架。"},{"pid":"e73136e41c398deecc9eca6b1f1d6abe23dd4cde","tid":211844,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b44951fbbe61cbdece254b62ed81042bc21b32c","tid":211844,"uid":99493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T04:47:46.000Z","msg":"【遺愛人間】好上司獲屍肝：要完成捐肝者心願<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170422&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56597045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170422%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56597045&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ef154ddf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170422%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56597045&h=5538abd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170422&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56597045</a><br />\n<br />\n好媽媽鄧桂思8日內兩獲好心人捐活肝及屍肝方得以續命，引起各界關注，但其實本港仍有90多名病人於換肝輪候冊上苦候屍肝，每年近3成病人等不及換肝已逝，令人惋惜。領導億元生意額團隊的地產代理高層吳國偉(Philip)是少數的幸運兒，他今年2月肝衰竭昏迷後曾命懸一線，全賴好心人捐出親人無價的屍肝，才得以活命，死過番生，令他重新思考金錢及生命的價值，尤其是救他性命的屍肝原來是來自一位等不及換心的病人。吳承諾若康復後會參與更多義務工作助人，更打算「帶著」寶貴的遺贈肝到英國旅遊，以助已逝的捐贈者可達成往英國的遺願。"},{"pid":"c94b354ca0b8759566632504c29083d2a638be1a","tid":211844,"uid":99493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"捐肝者 應該係基層 冇錢去英國旅行<br />\n<br />\n反而呢條地產高層大把錢 一好返就自己去英國玩<br />\n<br />\n應該要幫下 其他有需要的人"},{"pid":"6618f945a0e3a4cfb97f7d1a38b9af65a24365d1","tid":211844,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捐肝者 應該係基層 冇錢去英國旅行<br />\n<br />\n反而呢條地產高層大把錢 一好返就自己去英國玩<br />\n<br />\n應該要幫下 其他有需要的人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家佢咪幫左窮人去旅行LOR"}]}